    p.slds-text-heading_large Run your own workshop!

  .header.slds-grid.slds-wrap.slds-grid_align-space.slds-p-around_large.content.slds-grid_vertical-stretch
    .slds-size_1-of-3.slds-text-heading_medium
      img.slds-align_absolute-center(src='http://via.placeholder.com/350x350' alt='Community Leader Badge')
      p.slds-align_absolute-center.slds-m-vertical_medium At your company
    .slds-size_1-of-3.slds-text-heading_medium
      img.slds-align_absolute-center(src='http://via.placeholder.com/350x350' alt='Community Leader Badge')
      p.slds-align_absolute-center.slds-m-vertical_medium At your user group
    .slds-size_1-of-3.slds-text-heading_medium
      img.slds-align_absolute-center(src='http://via.placeholder.com/350x350' alt='Community Leader Badge')
      p.slds-align_absolute-center.slds-m-vertical_medium At a Salesforce Saturday

  .slds-p-around_large.header.slds-text-heading_small.slds-text-align_center

    p.slds-m-vertical_medium We provide the content guide and the scratch org deployer so you can get right to learning.
    p.slds-m-vertical_medium And if you let us know about your event in advance, we can send your our swag box.
    p.slds-m-vertical_medium Post about it on your Twitter or Instragram, and Salesforce will share it out.
    p.slds-m-vertical_medium Leading a workshop earns you our exclusive Community Leader badge.
    .slds-avatar.slds-avatar_circle.slds-avatar_large
      img(src='http://via.placeholder.com/350x350' alt='Community Leader Badge')

